This paper discusses the use of prediction markets for machine learning, which falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the concept of isoelastic utilities and wealth updates, which are topics related to game theory (cs.GT) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of market equilibrium computation and iterative algorithms also falls under the category of "Economics and Computation" (cs.EC) and "Data Structures and Algorithms" (cs.DS).
